      "bezeichnung": "Sustainability Impact Assessment",
      "kreditpunkte": 0,
      "planinhalt": "<p><strong>Learning Block 1:</strong> Sustainability Impact Assessment Methods This block focuses on frameworks and methodologies for evaluating the effectiveness of sustainability initiatives. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Learning Block 2:</strong> Startup exchange, reflection and impact assessment Insights by One-Planet Lab startups and applying methods in working groups. &nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Learning Block 3:</strong> Presentations and round table discussions with startups. This block focuses on the preparation and presentation of results, as well as the reflection of the outcomes together with the stakeholders in course of round tables.&nbsp;</p>",
      "empfLehrmittel": "<p>Lecture, Instructional Dialogue, Expert Exchange, Case Study Analysis, Guided Self-Study, Self-Study.</p>",
